  "identifier": "SB 1489",
  "title": "SB 1489 - Under this act, ivermectin and hydroxychloroquine tablets suitable for human use may be sold or purchased as over-the-counter medications in Missouri without a prescription or consultation with a pharmacist or other health care professional.\r\n\r\n\tThis act has an emergency clause.\r\n\r\n\tThis act is identical to HB 2293 (2026) and substantially similar to SB 1066 (2026), SB 1275 (2026), HB 1684 (2026), SB 744 (2025), and HB 2581 (2024).\r\nSARAH HASKINS",
